that have played here,

00:00:32.379 --> 00:00:33.833
so, we will do everything we can...

00:00:33.834 --> 00:00:39.856
in order to make everyone
related to Santos FC happy.

00:00:47.750 --> 00:00:51.468
I like to play offensively,

00:00:51.469 --> 00:00:52.893
I'm fast,

00:00:54.988 --> 00:00:57.485
I'm always trying to score,
but...

00:00:57.954 --> 00:01:01.192
I also know when it is time
to keep the ball under our possession,

00:01:01.874 --> 00:01:05.136
so, with my characteristics
and the other players we have,

00:01:05.137 --> 00:01:07.261
we hope we manage
to do a great season.

